的实例。下面我就对这句话做一个总结，举几个例子。这里的WSGI应用的功能都是返回请求的环境信息environ。'),(1136,181,'_aioseop_title','WSGI应用常见的几种写法-基本形式'),(1137,181,'_content_index_enable','1'),(1138,184,'posturl_add_url','yes'),(1139,184,'_edit_last','1'),(1140,184,'_edit_lock','1363718184:1'),(1152,184,'_aioseop_description','上一节中说到了WSGI应用的几种基本形式，这一节就来说一些高级的用法，所谓高级，我理解的也就是使用装饰器`@`，WebOb，以及中间件的形式，当然，还有一些更有意思的用法，比如Paste.Deploy这种载入WSGI应用的形式，我以后会做总结。还是和前篇[WSGI应用常见的几种写法-基本形式](http://op.wachang.net/blog/2012/12/wsgi-application-style-base/)一样，本文实现的WSGI应用都是一个回显请求环境信息的程序。'),(1153,184,'_aioseop_title','WSGI应用常见的几种写法-高级形式'),(1154,184,'_content_index_enable','1'),(1156,187,'posturl_add_url','yes'),(1157,187,'_edit_last','1'),(1158,187,'_edit_lock','1364974860:1'),(1172,190,'posturl_add_url','yes'),(1173,190,'_edit_last','1'),(1174,190,'_edit_lock','1364974791:1'),(1206,190,'_aioseop_description','ip是iproute2软件包里面的一个强大的网络配置工具，它能够替代一些传统的网络管理工具。例如：ifconfig、route 等。'),(1207,190,'_aioseop_title','Linux IP Command使用笔记'),(1208,198,'posturl_add_url','yes'),(1209,198,'_edit_last','1'),(1210,198,'_edit_lock','1364974874:1'),(1239,201,'posturl_add_url','yes'),(1240,201,'_edit_last','1'),(1241,201,'_edit_lock','1364974968:1'),(1278,205,'posturl_add_url','yes'),(1279,205,'_edit_last','1'),(1280,205,'_edit_lock','1367477256:1'),(1281,206,'posturl_add_url','yes'),(1282,206,'_edit_last','1'),(1283,206,'_edit_lock','1364653839:1'),(1284,208,'posturl_add_url','yes'),(1285,208,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(1286,208,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(1287,208,'_menu_item_object_id','206'),(1288,208,'_menu_item_object','page'),(1289,208,'_menu_item_target',''),(1290,208,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(1291,208,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(1292,208,'_menu_item_url',''),(1293,209,'posturl_add_url','yes'),(1294,209,'_edit_last','1'),(1295,209,'_edit_lock','1365314537:1'),(1296,211,'posturl_add_url','yes'),(1297,211,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(1298,211,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(1299,211,'_menu_item_object_id','209'),(1300,2